<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3954635>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Living Leptobrachella wulingensis sp. nov. from Tianzishan Nature Reserve, individuals not collected. (A) Young metamorph toad with remnants of its tadpole tail, sitting on a rock; (B) and (C) adult individuals sitting on wet forest floor; (D) female toad laying on the ground. Photos by Tianyu Qian on August (A) and September (B, C and D) in 2019." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3954635/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3954631>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Dorsal and ventral view of living paratypes of Leptobrachela wulingensis sp. nov showing different body sizes. (A, K) CSUFT 200, adult male; (B, L) CSUFT 180, adult male; (C, M) CSUFT 193, adult male; (D, N) CSUFT 179, adult male; (E, O) CSUFT 202, subadult female; (F, P) CSUFT 178, subadult female; (G, Q) CSUFT 203, subadult female; (H, R) CSUFT 204, subadult female; (I, S) CSUFT 177, adult female; (J, T) CSUFT 194, adult female." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3954631/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3954627>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Bayesian inference tree of Leptobrachella species with Bayesian posterior probabilities (BPP) and maximum-likelihood (ML) bootstrap values, based on partial sequences of the mitochondrial 16S rRNA gene. Leptobrachium cf. chapaense and Megophrys major were used as outgroups. Black circles are nodes supported by BPP and ML values greater than 0.94 or 70, respectively. Gray circles are nodes supported only by ML values greater than 70. White circles are nodes supported only by BPP values greater than 0.94." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3954627/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3954633>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Iris coloration of paratypes of Leptobrachella wulingensis sp. nov.: (A) CSUFT 178; (B) CSUFT 180; (C) CSUFT 177; (D) CSUFT 194; (E) CSUFT 193; (F) CSUFT 200; (G) CSUFT 204; (H) CSUFT 179; (I) CSUFT 202; (J) CSUFT 203." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3954633/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3954629>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Holotype of Leptobrachella wulingensis sp. nov. (CSUFT 201, adult female) in life: (A) lateral view, (B) iris, (C) ventral view, (D) volar view of left hand, (E) plantar view of right foot, and (F) black spots on flanks." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3954629/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

